      "author": "Txoldi",
      "description": "Version 1.0.0 of the Last.fm integration for Obsidian\r\n\r\n# Features\r\n\r\n- Recent Scrobbles Viewer\r\n\r\nFetch and display your latest scrobbles directly inside Obsidian.\r\n\r\n- Top Tracks / Albums / Artists\r\n\r\nSupports all official Last.fm time periods (7day → overall)\r\nConfigurable result limit.\r\n\r\n- Weekly Charts (Range Mode)\r\n\r\nBrowse historical weekly charts using valid Last.fm “from / to” ranges.\r\n\r\n- Note Generation\r\n\r\nCreate formatted Markdown notes for:\r\n\r\nRecent scrobbles\r\nTop tracks / artists / albums\r\nWeekly charts\r\nIncludes album art where available.\r\n\r\n- UI Modal with Tabs\r\n\r\nClean, user-friendly modal navigation for all features.\r\n\r\n- Custom Note Folder Setting\r\n\r\nChoose where generated notes should be created.",
